Node-docker repository

Node Steps:
1. npm init
2. npm install express
3. npm install nodemon --save-dev
4. node index.js

Docker Steps:
1. docker build -t node-app-image . 
2. docker run -d -p3000:3000 --name node-app node-app-image
3. docker exec -it node-app bash
4. docker rm -f node-app
5. docker run -v /$(pwd):/app -v /app/node_mudules -d -p3000:3000 --name node-app node-app-image